reviewText: Nice, but very basic and the video must be from the early 90's.

I was shocked to find that it looks to be a video from the 80's transferred from VHS to DVD.  I gave it 3 stars because I haven't actually watched it through.  I will do a follow-up review on the content once I watch it, but I would recommend looking at the VOL. I and VOL.II individually and reading the review before purchasing.
